This is a list of the 50 oldest Ministers-President of Germany since 1945 by longevity . The oldest actuelly governing Ministers-President is the one from Sachsen-Anhalt : Wolfgang B hmer (born 27. January 1936). Where the person in question is still living, the longevity is calculated up to June 13, 2008.
